StarUI Inventory - FormIDs
==========================

This is a pure text file and simply contains lists of FormIDs, so you can put those into the StarUI Inventory.ini to ignore certain items for mass-transfering.

Thanks to the user user ajantaju, who collected all these FormIDs from the plugin files! 

Note: You need to add this to the setting sMassTransferIgnoreFormIDs. If you want to include multiple lists make sure to add a comma between!
